title: 10/11/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 10/11/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to the MMQB's Albert Breer and discusses whether Trevon Diggs has a chance at winning the Defensive Player of the Year. The voice of the SEC Paul Finebaum tells us who he thinks the obvious choice for USC is. Plus, Former NFL QB Carson Palmer explains why he's all in on the Chargers.
